reviewText: My Son Lawrence Inglee is the producer and the person who talked Jerry Lewis into doing what will be a great drama staring Jerry Lewis! He and his wife Jenny are now in Cannes getting ready to with Jerry Lewis about to give the world his greatest film ever!! What else can I say except look up my son or Max Rose and you will know Jerry's best work ever!
I just love The Cemetery Club and thnx  to Amazon I finally found this forgotten Movie.  Thank you-
I loved the movie.  The disc is mislabeled.  There is only one disc.  The movie is labeled on the opposite side.

Wonderful double DVD.  The Cemetery Club is heartwarming and funny with some sad thrown in to balance it out.  Just like real life.
Funny Bones is another wonderful Jerry Lewis comedy.

I would recommend this seller.
Cemetery Club is one of my favorite movies.  That's why I ordered it.  I had no desire to see Funny Bones and have no idea why you would group  these two movies together!
Bought primarily for "The Cemetery Club."  Loved it.  Haven't watched the other film yet.
